title: 9-9-14 Apple iPhone 6 Watch Special Event Keynote
description: I'm pretty annoyed how this has been completely unwatchable the entire day, when it was live, and even though it ended hours ago it still cant be streamed. Anyway, this is the HD file hosted on Apple's servers that we should be able to watch if their website worked correctly at ALL. seriously I must have tried 7 different devices and multiple browsers before ripping this file directly from the server. Very frustrating. Enjoy.
